"{\"uid\": \"the42.ie-aidan-walsh-olympic-boxing-qualifier-6395073-May2024\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"LAST UPDATE|31 May 2024 GR\\u00c1INNE WALSH WILL fight for Olympic qualification on Sunday morning after coming through her last-16 bout in the 66kg division in style on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 172, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LAST UPDATE|31 May 2024 GR\\u00c1INNE WALSH\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 37}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic qualification\", \"from\": 53, \"to\": 74}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday morning\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 92}, {\"ngram\": \"her last-16 bout\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 130}, {\"ngram\": \"the 66kg division\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 151}, {\"ngram\": \"style\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Aidan Walsh will have to win a four-man box-off this weekend to book his ticket to Paris after two point deductions cost him in the final Olympic qualification tournament in Bangkok.\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aidan_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.1578068126828092e-11, \"text\": \"Aidan Walsh\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aidan_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aidan_Walsh\"}, {\"begin\": 261, \"end\": 266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997339728, \"rank\": 2.661894739248305e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"score\": 0.9999998892271894, \"rank\": 5.6449471043870026e-08, \"text\": \"Bangkok\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a four-man box-off\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 225}, {\"ngram\": \"his ticket\", \"from\": 247, \"to\": 257}, {\"ngram\": \"two point deductions\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"the final Olympic qualification tournament\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tokyo bronze medallist lost a 4-1 split decision to Jordanian Zeyad Eashash, which was decided by public warnings in the second and third rounds for excessive holding.\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 366, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999976703293, \"rank\": 2.3281726929974664e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 4-1 split decision\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"Jordanian Zeyad Eashash\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"public warnings\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"the second and third rounds\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"excessive holding\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Belfast light middleweight's hopes of becoming a two-time Olympian now rest on the 71kg box-off, where he must win two bouts this weekend to secure the fifth and final qualification berth.\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 539, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"score\": 0.9999994699461735, \"rank\": 4.577579653451609e-07, \"text\": \"Belfast\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\"}, {\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999980768675716, \"rank\": 1.923136148090933e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 71kg box-off\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"two bouts\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 663}, {\"ngram\": \"the fifth and final qualification berth\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Walsh appeared well placed after a tactical first round saw him emerge on top of all five judges' scorecards.\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Walsh\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"a tactical first round\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"all five judges' scorecards\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The back-foot fighter was twice warned, however, by the Guatemalan referee over a lack of engagement.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The back-foot fighter\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"the Guatemalan referee\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"engagement\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That forced a change of approach as the second round wore on and once Eashash began to press forward, Walsh found himself in trouble.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 1075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a change\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"approach\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"the second round\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"Eashash\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"Walsh\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"trouble\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement He received a public warning for excessive holding but still did enough to tie the round 9-9 with three judges (while the other two went 10-8 for Eashash) and held a narrow lead into the third.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a public warning\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"excessive holding\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"three judges\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"Eashash\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"a narrow lead\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1268}, {\"ngram\": \"the third\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Walsh continued to be spoken to by the referee and when he was again called for holding, it led to a public warning and another point docked.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Walsh\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"the referee\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"holding\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"a public warning\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"another point\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being compelled to trade toe-to-toe favoured the Jordanian and he did enough, winning on all but one scorecard: 29-26, 29-26, 28-27, 28-27, 27-28.\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toe\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"toe\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"the Jordanian\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"all but one scorecard\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Tullamore's Gr\\u00e1inne Walsh is just one win from making her Olympic debut after she earned a unanimous decision over Ivorian Sedia Sanogo in the 66kg last 16.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tullamore\", \"score\": 0.9999999999840838, \"rank\": 1.5843947552410152e-11, \"text\": \"Tullamore\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tullamore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tullamore\"}, {\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res